description: Outstanding Value! Spacious 2 Br 2.5 Ba Bi-Level (Floors 2&3) condominium. Large living room with roaring gas fireplace. Additional alcove makes for a great home office, Ina Garten kitchen with granite & stainless steel appliances. 2 sizeable bedrooms upstairs, each with ensuite bath. Downstairs powder room perfect for guests. Glistening hardwood floors and high ceilings throughout. Zoned heating & cooling, in-unit laundry, balcony. Professionally managed building with healthy reserves. Pet friendly. Great for commuters, seconds to Andrew Square T Station and minutes from downtown and the airport. Next to exciting Washington Village development with its brand new restaurants, retail stores and parks.
